data.title: List of people from Lincoln, Nebraska
data.text: List of people from Lincoln, Nebraska alphabetical order Name DOB DOD Career Notability Fred Abel 1903 1980 Athlete NFL player Hazel Abel 1888 1966 Teacher and politician First woman from Nebraska elected to serve in U.S. Senate Nancy C. Andreasen 1938 Neuroscientist One of world's foremost authorities on schizophrenia Emma M.
